description:
The complete IDE crafted for Gophers


GoLand 2024.3 is now available!
The release comes with new IDE functionality and support for new Go features, including:

- New inspection for cyclic imports
- Management of multiple Go services and configurations in a single UI
- Performance improvements: Faster opening of larger projects
- String() object view in debugger
- Emulate terminal in output console option
- Multiple enchancements for Kubernetes
- Multiple enchancements for Terraform and support for OpenTofu
For a complete rundown of the new features, visit our What's New page.
